Changes made to the py2app package
in /System/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/2.7/Extras/lib/python

- new recipe for mpl_toolkits as mpltk.py (recipes/mpltk.py, recipes/mpltk_prescript.py, recipes/__init__.py)
- new command to add to boot to set siren data path (bootstrap/custom_defs.py)
- skip some data files when copying, etc (build_app.py) 

Also changed shutils copy function to prevent flag setting (not allowed)
